<h1> Product Roadmap </h1>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
    <h2>Overview:</h2>
     <p> The Product Roadmap is used to identify and track what needs to be delivered to create value for the customer. It displays how the product will resolve the
problem or fulfill the customers' unmet needs and shows the value that is created for both customers and stakeholders.
     Prior to completing the Product Roadmap, we recommend completing the How Might We Play, Customer Empathy Map, Crazy 8's, Solution Art Gallery, Value Proposition Map, and Customer Journey. You should have already
   identified the goal of your product, the problem you are trying to solve, the potential solution, and the value created for the customer. </p>
      </div>
  </div>

